About 95% done with the new studio. I’ve been working on this new spot for over 10 months and I’m so excited to finally be in here working. I worked 7 days a week putting in 12-16 hour days for 10 years to be able to do this. Im grateful to have this opportunity and supportive collectors. In May of 2022 local code enforcement change the zoning codes and made it illegal to blow glass on your property and made a requirement for all glass blowing to be conducted on a M1 Zoned industrial land. So instead of fighting them in court to rezone my land I decided to just play ball and invest in myself and this new studio. Thanks for checking it out and making this possible ❤️🙏🏻 #glassblowing

Serum over Chartreuse 🌸🌼 Tube #3 inspired by the traditional beaker tube. I wanted to create a recycler tube that had a silhouette of a beaker using the drain lines. The perc in this piece starts with a 6 hole 20mm shower head in a 50mm can, the reduces down to 32mm with 2, 6 hole 20mm disc, then opens back up to 38mm and into the splash guard and over flow. I definitely could have put more water in this poece but I was in a rush. More function videos coming and many more Tubes 😃 #science #lab #tech #research #tedtalk

Dry pipe concept from yesterdays work. It’s always fun to try someone new each day in the studio. This piece is inspired by the Vestpocket style pipe but it’s not flat on either side, I kept it round making it feel like your holding a ball when smoking it. This is a super comfortable piece to hold and smoke and I’m think i need to do an encalmo Version. I also have a few my dry pipe concepts coming up and I’m excited to share.  #pipe #art #concept

Little sneak peek of the 30 inch triple diffused flower tube with over 200 encalmo sections with endless custom color blends. Next step is the flair the foot then she’s done. This is an absurd amount of work even the 3 percs are full encalmo and the splash guard. I also added clear windows by the main perc and splash guard so you could see the encalmo work on them.  This has been one of the most challenging builds in a wile and I learned a tone. Crazy man hours in this piece, I had @chad_wook_glass stacking color for the past couple weeks and then I took the sections of 25mm encalmo tube and condensed it down and brought it all out to 60mm. Very excited to see this one tomorrow morning. #science #art #research #explorepage #glassart #encalmo

So much work in this tube I probably could have made 8-9 different RBR’s our of the prep that went into this thing. Over 200 encalmos with endless custom color blends. It’s 28 inches tall, 18mm joint , 52mm Body , 32mm neck , 12 hole gridded shower head perc 2x 6 slit diffusers, and splash guard. Excited to keep pushing the limits with my team.
